<subSubSection pageId="46" pageNumber="530" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="46.[167,1376,1813,2834]" pageId="46" pageNumber="530">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[169,509,2642,2675]" pageId="46" pageNumber="530">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCNRed List. Orces’s Longtongued Batis listed as critically endangered in 
<collectingCountry box="[834,950,2682,2715]" name="Ecuador" pageId="46" pageNumber="530">Ecuador</collectingCountry>
. It is a rare and poorly known. Only known locality is the Cotacachi-Cayapas Ecological Reserve. Deforestation and consequent problems of habitat loss and fragmentation are probably main threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
